name: 2012 Yule Ball Poster
description: This is a poster that was made for the 2012 Yule Balls in Brooklyn and Boston. Designed and screenprinted by Dustin Williams, these are from a signed edition of 100 posters. They are printed with white and silver paint on heavy chipboard. Posters will ship in flat mailers. Dimensions are 12" x 17".

name: 2012 Snow Ball Poster
description: This is a poster that was made for the 2012 Snow Ball in Edinburgh, Scotland. Designed and screenprinted by Dustin Williams, these are from a signed edition of 100 posters. They are printed with white and silver paint on heavy chipboard. Posters will ship in flat mailers. Dimensions are 11.5" x 16.5"
